WEBVTT

00:03:27.795 --> 00:03:33.365
They believed that every case of ghosts
that they had investigated so far

00:03:33.389 --> 00:03:35.564
had been explained away by science.

00:03:35.588 --> 00:03:39.532
And I was like, "OK, smart guys,
this is what's happening to me,

00:03:39.556 --> 00:03:43.631
and if you have an explanation for me,
I would love to hear it."

00:03:43.655 --> 00:03:46.865
And one of them said, "OK.

00:03:46.889 --> 00:03:50.975
Um, have you heard
of carbon monoxide poisoning?"

00:03:52.877 --> 00:03:57.339
And I said, "Yeah.

00:03:57.363 --> 00:04:00.710
Like, gas poisoning?"